                    "first_character_index": 36826,
                    "last_character_index": 38350
                }
            ],
            "answer": "The fused batched MoE layer in vLLM returns the activations in the following format:\n\n- A tensor of shape `(num_experts, max_tokens, K)`, where `num_experts` is the number of experts, `max_tokens` is the maximum number of tokens, and `K` is the number of features per token.\n\nThis format is used in the batched MoE implementation, where the activations are grouped by experts and the tokens that subscribe to the same expert are batched together."
