            ],
            "answer": "The values in `cudagraph_inputs_embeds` are determined by whether the model is enabled to use prompt embeddings (`model_config.enable_prompt_embeds`) and whether the model is in an encoder-decoder mode (`is_encoder_decoder_model`). If `model_config.enable_prompt_embeds` is `True`, then `cudagraph_inputs_embeds` will include `True` for the input embeddings, and `False` for the output embeddings. If `model_config.enable_prompt_embeds` is `False`, then `cudagraph_inputs_embeds` will include `False` for the input embeddings and `True` for the output embeddings."
